# Milestone NN: Descriptive Name

## Goal

Describe the slice of testbench scaffolding this milestone lands.
Typical examples: "payload-aware Sequencers"; "Drivers + handshake
wiring"; "Monitors per observable port"; "Scoreboards + reference
model"; "`SimEnvBuilder` helper + basic data-flow smoke test".

## Tasks

Each task names a concrete artifact (Rust file or symbol under
`tests/`). At most 10 `- [ ]` rows per file
(`docs/impl-plan/plan-management.md` enforces the cap).

- [ ] `tests/<file_or_helper>::<symbol>` -- one-line purpose
  - mirrors: `lib:examples/<NN-name>/test/<file>`
  - traces to: `<test-plan.md section, spec section, or
    decomposition operation>`

- [ ] `tests/<file_or_helper>::<symbol>` -- one-line purpose
